snippet.title: CrankVenture Capitalist Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is my next game for the Playdate! It is out now as part of the Uncrank'd Fun in The Sun bundle. 

Crank, wait, purchase and rescue your mom from the kidnappers, bankers and aliens! You can do it! This is an idle incremental game with both a story and an endless mode.  There is a secret in the game that I will reveal once someone can show that they've gotten to level 100 in the endless mode! 

https://irishjiminy.itch.io/crankventure-capitalist
